### GET POST TESTS
### ========================================

### Get Post by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Public Feed
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/feed?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Posts by User ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/user/1?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Posts by Group ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/posts/group/5?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

